originalText.text: Angela has been amazing. I been seeing her for a couple of weeks for my Type 2 diabetes and she gives the best recommendations. She constantly checks on you and is always available on chat if I have questions in regards to my food choices. This journey has been challenging for me, and Angela puts me at ease with her support and guidance. She is also very patient and kind. I am so happy to be working with her. Thank you Angela.

originalText.text:
I have had the privilege of working with Angela Houlie for the past six months. She is a true expert in her field, and her guidance has not only transformed my dietary habits but also significantly improved my overall quality of life.

One of the aspects I appreciate most about Angela is her personalized approach. She took the time to get to know me, my lifestyle, and my specific health goals before tailoring a nutrition plan that was both realistic and effective. This individualized approach made all the difference for me, as it ensured that I never felt like I was following a one-size-fits-all diet but rather a plan that was uniquely designed to suit my needs.

Angela is a great motivator. She has celebrated my successes, no matter how small, and encouraged me to stay committed to my goals. Her positive attitude created an empowering environment that helped me stay focused and confident in my ability to make positive changes.

In just six months, I have witnessed remarkable improvements in my health. I have more energy, my health issues have significantly improved, and I've achieved a healthier body weight without feeling deprived or overwhelmed.

I highly recommend Angela Houlie to anyone seeking guidance on their nutrition journey!!
